My father wrote to Delhi Indian Home Office to send either proof or his original Passport he surrendered 3 years ago but have not received any reply . What is annoying is most of the community leaders know of the difficulty but despite attending meetings and function with Indian High Commissioner and the staff none have raised the issue that it is very unfair to discard completely a British Passport stating that the person is born in India .
